{
  "stem": "3103.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They send it to Milwaukee, thinking of all the breweries that my father will be able to get with no problem any job.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when they came in, they prepare a two bedroom apartment with welcome cakes, with beds, with blankets, with clothing, with groceries in the refrigerator.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I cried over that letter months.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I couldn't believe that's true.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But that's what the country can do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "If you can appreciate your freedom, and you have your goals, the sky was the limit.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You could accomplish whatever you want to in this great, beautiful country we are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was yet in Germany.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And actually, my father bought a few machines that they will produce like the type of a soft drink, like Coca-Cola, but made from fruit.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because besides the beer, he had this at home also to do the same thing in Israel, but not beer.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Bernie, my husband, as a survivor, the only one from the family, had no desire to go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He had no desire to go to Israel because, I tell you what, at the time, the people are very pushy at those days in Israel.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They're aggressive.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he is not this kind of a type of a person.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He's not aggressive.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He cannot stretch his elbows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he thought he's never going to make it there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I made my $50 on the ship called-- it was a military ship-- You had to tell what you did before.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said I'm a dentist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My husband was already a physician.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had to do a job, help it out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they opened for me one on the deck a room.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had all equipment for dentistry.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was for the sailors.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, it was never opened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I told them I'm a dentist.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
